  <T n="name">0x4FE04BC8<!--String: "Adding Sims & Relationships"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_AddingSimsAndRelationships_1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:46f250dd7357b8b5</T>
      <T n="text">0x6B8D32A<!--String: "Households can have up to <b><font color='#199C2C'>8 Sims</font></b>! Add more Sims by clicking on the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Add a Sim</font></b> button.\n\nChoose <b><font color='#199C2C'>Add New Sim</font></b> to randomize a new Sim to customize. If you want some help setting up a backstory and personality for your new Sim, select <b><font color='#199C2C'>Add Sim via a Story</font></b>."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_AddingSimsAndRelationships_2.png" n="image">2f7d0004:00000000:46f250dd7357b8b6</T>
      <T n="text">0xE314FCCE<!--String: "To create a Sim that looks like one of the existing Sims in the household, you can select<b><font color='#199C2C'> Play with Genetics</font></b>. \n\nSelect a <b><font color='#199C2C'>starting Sim</font></b> (or Sims), what kind of <b><font color='#199C2C'>relative</font></b> you want to add (Parent, Child, or Sibling), the new Sim’s <b><font color='#199C2C'>age</font></b> and <b><font color='#199C2C'>gender</font></b>, and then hit <b><font color='#199C2C'>Randomize</font></b> until you’re happy! Don’t forget to <b><font color='#199C2C'>Confirm</font></b>. "--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_AddingSimsAndRelationships_3.png" n="image">2f7d0004:00000000:46f250dd7357b8b7</T>
      <T n="text">0xF047CA92<!--String: "You can set <b><font color='#199C2C'>Relationships</font></b> between the Sims in your household in the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Household Relationships</font></b> menu in the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Identity</font></b> panel."--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
